{"tid":353710,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[導演介紹] 挑戰道德倫理宗教的Lars von Trier","createTime":"2017-08-10T00:04:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-06T03:32:50.000Z","uid":78390,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eb632d08c3cd9531bd5e5660e4e57281918047c1","tid":353710,"uid":78390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T00:04:15.000Z","msg":"做到康城電影節嘅常客從來都不容易<br />\n每一部新作都有獨特創新風格<br />\n而且大膽挑戰各種議題 （尤其女性）睇完都不禁沉思 諗諗解角色的動機同電影當中意義<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/kt2oizfa\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fkt2oizfa&h=50c25931&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nNymphomaniac Vol.1 and Vol.2<br />\n一部應該係咸片但其實有深道的電影<br />\n透過兩人對話去了解性上癮的女生的經過 同性嘅議題<br />\n電影特別表達手法 令到故事更有韻味<br />\n真心慢慢睇到最後結局 因為Lars 啲戲真係要睇結尾<br />\nUma Thurman 個part最正<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/wefsokpl\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fwefsokpl&h=8e788f0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDogville<br />\nQuentin Tarantino 都話係21世紀最好嘅劇<br />\n呢部成三粒鐘但沒有冷場<br />\n跟隨Nicole Kidman走進一個看似正常的小城<br />\n一步一步踩入一個永無止境只有人性的地方<br />\n看似一部舞台劇 卻是一個别有心裁的劇場設計<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/cw8dfa4o\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fcw8dfa4o&h=f427fc96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/3kz0rja6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F3kz0rja6&h=2fa3dee4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAnti-Christ <br />\n呢部首映禮有四條友睇到暈咗<br />\n不過幾深 都想求解釋<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/cx3sv6ey\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fcx3sv6ey&h=f7534b4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMelancholia<br />\n拍得最美的一部<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ibhps821\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fibhps821&h=e759f77e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDancer in the Dark<br />\n呢部算係俾正常人睇<br />\n係一部音樂電影 啲角色會無啦啦唱歌<br />\n以一個單純傻女角度去看這個世界 一直相信這個世界係好<br />\n都一部極危險但值得一看的電影<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/jhbqvg54\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fjhbqvg54&h=1a033211&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBreaking the Waves <br />\n係我睇過最難受嘅電影<br />\n簡直將道德倫理顛倒<br />\n加上評論神與教堂區別<br />\n令我認為Lars von Trier最大膽之作<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/b7xvol3j\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fb7xvol3j&h=e7e76b88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以上電影都會令人情緒不安 敬請家長留意"},{"pid":"0b291da94f0b2cf71d8f14c02168de0d8c892df0","tid":353710,"uid":58352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T00:07:47.000Z","msg":"正post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8581cbe260ce5431a00d12d7c5737687cc0598c3","tid":353710,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T02:25:44.000Z","msg":"唔係講笑 Anti-Christ真係睇到暈左一暈<br />\n好大衝擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84378e85ff283e878e247a41daf6a5adbbf72b77","tid":353710,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T02:27:39.000Z","msg":"Nymphomaniac 我係鍾意vol 1多過vol 2"},{"pid":"f30f9c8e8e9d3883db10d781097c204711cd8b25","tid":353710,"uid":78390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T02:54:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Nymphomaniac 我係鍾意vol 1多過vol 2</blockquote><br />\nVol. 2真係冇咁好睇<br />\n不過有啲位都寫得比Vol. 1 好難受<br />\n個part審個男人真係睇到好嬲 但Lars寫到好似佢有苦衷 都唔知點解佢咁諗好痴線<br />\n結局我簡直發咗癲"},{"pid":"1320eb17b8cabc2cfa6731d37814503867e069ec","tid":353710,"uid":4586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T03:12:43.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"922708243d17143d2f6995ad60136ffe065ade25","tid":353710,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T07:15:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Nymphomaniac 我係鍾意vol 1多過vol 2</blockquote><br />\nVol. 2真係冇咁好睇<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不過有啲位都寫得比Vol. 1 好難受</span><br />\n個part審個男人真係睇到好嬲 但Lars寫到好似佢有苦衷 都唔知點解佢咁諗好痴線<br />\n結局我簡直發咗癲</blockquote><br />\n同意 以為joe獲得救贖，無之餘仲愈踩愈深<br />\nvol 2果種難受睇到人好壓抑"},{"pid":"9fbce9a52657077796442addbaa586326a2e0e99","tid":353710,"uid":78390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T03:32:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/06/113147_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F06%2F113147_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=952dc511&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今年有好戲"},{"pid":"bf0f1f9386e072f2fae3309dc7e7fd39d74745da","tid":353710,"uid":78390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T03:32:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/06/113235_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F06%2F113235_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=86096b17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n已經好不安"}]}